data.description: Many updates in this Popular area Overland Hills home! 3br/2bath/ 2 car with many updates to enjoy. New LVP flooring on main floor, and fresh paint in many areas!! Granite counters accented by glass tile backslash in kitchen with island, eat in dining, and slider to deck area with built in blinds for privacy! Stainless kitchen appliances as well as washer and dryer.  Gas log fireplace for those chilly winter nights. Both bath areas have been tastefully updated with modern finishes.  High Efficiency furnace 2012. Vinyl windows, permanent siding and roof replaced in 2017. Water heater 2022. Fully fenced yard for your enjoyment. All of the heavy lifting has been done and the only lifting for you to do is moving in!! Schedule today for your private showing.
